# 🤖 Telegram String Session Generator Bot

A production-ready Telegram bot for generating Pyrogram string sessions securely with advanced features, admin controls, and one-click deployment on Render.

[![Deploy to Render](https://render.com/images/deploy-to-render-button.svg)](https://render.com/deploy)

---

## ✨ Features

### 🔐 Core Features
- Generate Pyrogram string sessions securely
- Support for phone number, OTP, and 2FA verification
- Real-time input validation with clear error messages
- Auto-delete sensitive messages after 10 minutes
- No storage of credentials or sessions

### 🛡️ Security
- Rate limiting to prevent abuse
- Session timeout for inactive users
- Automatic cleanup of sensitive data
- No logging of passwords or OTPs
- Secure state management

### 👥 Admin Features
- `/stats` - View bot statistics
- `/users` - List all users
- `/broadcast` - Send messages to all users
- Admin-only commands protection

### 🚀 Deployment
- One-click deployment on Render
- GitHub integration
- Health check endpoints
- Auto-deploy on push
- Environment variable management

---

## 📋 Prerequisites

- Python 3.11 or higher
- Telegram Bot Token (from [@BotFather](https://t.me/BotFather))
- Telegram API ID & Hash (from [my.telegram.org](https://my.telegram.org))
- GitHub account (for deployment)
- Render account (for hosting)

