🐛 Troubleshooting

Common Issues and Solutions

1. Bot Not Starting

```
❌ ERROR: BOT_TOKEN is required!
```

Solution: Set BOT_TOKEN in environment variables.

---

2. Admin Commands Not Working

```
⛔ You are not authorized to use this command.
```

Solution: Ensure your Telegram ID is in ADMIN_IDS.

---

3. Rate Limit Error

```
⚠️ Rate Limit Exceeded
```

Solution: Wait for rate limit period to reset or increase RATE_LIMIT.

---

4. Invalid API Credentials

```
❌ Invalid API_ID or API_HASH
```

Solution: Check API credentials from my.telegram.org.

---

5. Session Timeout

```
⏳ Session expired
```

Solution: Start again with /generate within timeout period.

---

6. Flood Wait

```
⏳ Flood Wait: 30 seconds
```

Solution: Wait for the specified time before retrying.

